    "id": "substack-https://palakmathur.substack.com/p/homesick",
    "title": "Homesick",
    "link": "https://palakmathur.substack.com/p/homesick",
    "content": "Text within this block will maintain its original spacing when published I yearn for a home, I yearn for a time, I yearn for the life that exists no longer. I want to live those days once more, in the hope it will make me feel stronger. I yearn for that room, I yearn for that terrace, I yearn for that way of living that exists no longer. I yearn to live it once more, in the hope it will make me feel stronger. I yearn for those skies, I yearn for those stars, I yearn for those nights that exist no longer. I yearn to stand beneath them once more, in the hope it will make me feel stronger. I yearn for all this and more, to live those memories again. That place exists, and yet it doesn\u2019t. That time survives only in memory. I hope these memories never fade, I hope those faces never blur. Homesickness, image of a house with a bed and from window the view of Taj Mahal blurred in setting sun Thanks for reading Vichar Vahak - Stories and Musings! Subscribe for free to receive new posts and support my work.",
